trans-unit.source: Iterates over all following nodes according to the XPath following-axis rules.
trans-unit.target: Går over alle følgende noder i samsvar med XPath følgende akser reglene.

trans-unit.source: According to the XPath following-axis rules, the descendants are not included, even though they follow the starting node in document order.
trans-unit.target: I samsvar med XPath følgende akser reglene inkluderes underordnede ikke, selv om de følger noden Start i dokumentrekkefølgen.

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: Status for navigatoren endringer bare hvis den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.MoveNext%2A>metoden har returnert `true`.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator to the next following node.
trans-unit.target: Plasserer iterator til neste følgende node.

trans-unit.source: If the iterator was set to the next following node, the MoveNext method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.Current%2A> property to the current result navigator; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Hvis iterator ble satt til neste følgende node, metoden MoveNext angir den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.Current%2A>egenskapen gjeldende resultatet navigatoren; ellers den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.Current%2A>egenskapen forblir uendret.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathFollowingIterator.Current%2A>
